      "title": "Estimated daily cost (USD) - yesterday",
      "type": "stat",
      "description": "From ce:GetCostAndUsage, filtered to Application=uk-clearing-advisor cost allocation tag (this account also runs unrelated workloads, so account-level billing would be meaningless here). Published daily by the CostReporter Lambda. Cost Explorer data lags ~24h, so this always reflects yesterday, not today.",
